snippet.title: The Oil Blue: Steam Legacy Edition Trailer
snippet.description: The Oil Blue launches for the first time on Steam with all new extras including Steam Trading Cards, Achievements, the game's soundtrack by Jonathan Geer in MP3/FLAC formats and more! View the Steam page here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/386700
